We are honored to be featured in the National Geographic Traveller Spa & Wellness Collection! This recognition is a testament to our commitment to providing exceptional wellness experiences.

A heartfelt thank you to our wonderful guests for your trust and support—this wouldn’t be possible without you! 💖 We look forward to continuing to be your sanctuary for relaxation and rejuvenation.

#Gratitude #SpaExcellence #NationalGeographicTraveller #WellnessJourney

We are pleased to share that we have been voted as Trip Advisor’s Traveler’s Choice Awards Winner 2024 yet again.

At Sawadhee, we aim to provide our guests with an unparalleled experience wherein they can relax, refresh and rejuvenate themselves. We aim to create a space for our guests to unwind and connect with themselves, look after themselves and prioritise their wellbeing. This award is a testament to that!

We look forward to hosting you and helping you relax!
